\c 2
\s Jehovha anotuka Israeri
\p
\v 1 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakauya kwandiri, richiti,
\v 2 Enda, undodana munzeve dzaveJerusarema, uti zvanzi naJehovha, Ndakarangarira pamusoro pako hunyoro hwohuduku hwako norudo rwenguva yokuwanikwa kwako, kuti wakanditevera murenje, munyika yakange isina kudzvarwa.
\v 3 Israeri vakange vari rudzi rutsvene kuna Jehovha, zvibereko zvitsva zvaakazviwanira; vese vanomudya vachava nemhosva; vachawirwa nezvakaipa ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\p
\v 4 Inzwai shoko raJehovha, imwi imba yaJakove, nemhuri dzose dzeimba yaIsraeri,
\v 5 Zvanzi naJehovha, Madzibaba enyu akawana zvisakarurama zvipiko kwandiri, zvavakaenda kure neni, zvavakatevera zvisina maturo, ivo vamene vakava vasina maturo?
\v 6 Uye havana kureva, vachiti, Uripiko Jehovha wakatibudisa panyika yeEgipita, akatifambisa murenje, munyika ina masango namakomba, munyika yakaoma neyomumvuri worufu, munyika isingafambi nomunhu achipfuurapo, musingagari munhu?
\v 7 Ndakakusvitsai munyika ineminda yakaorera, kuti mudye zvibereko zvayo nezvakanaka zvayo; asi makati mapinda, mukasvibisa nyika yangu, mukaita nhaka yangu chinhu chinonyangadza.
\v 8 Vapristi havana kuti, Jehovha uripiko? Vaifambisa mirairo vakange vasingandizivi, vafudzi vaindidarikira, vaporofita vaiporofitira Bhaari, vachitevera zvinhu zvisingabatsiri.
\p
\v 9 Saka zvanzi naJehovha, Ndicharamba ndichikakavara nemi, ndichakakavara navana vavana venyu.
\v 10 Nokuti yambukirai kuzviwi zveKitimi, muone; tumai vanhu Kedhari, mufungisise zvakanaka, muone kana kwakambovapo chinhu chakadai.
\v 11 Ko rudzi ruripo rwakatsinhanhisa vamwari varwo, ivo vasati vari vamwari here? Asi vanhu vangu vakatsinhanisa kukudzwa kwavo nezvinhu zvisingabatsiri.
\v 12 Shamiswa nechinhu ichi, iwe denga rose, utye zvikuru, uvhunduswe kwazvo ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\v 13 Nokuti vanhu vangu vakaita zvinhu zviviri zvakaipa. Vakandisiya, ini tsime remvura mhenyu, vakazvicherera mativi, mativi akaputsika, asingagoni kuchengeta mvura.
\v 14 Israeri muranda here? Ko ndiye muranda wakaberekerwa mumba matenzi wake here? Ko zvino wapambwa seiko?
\v 15 Vana veshumba vakamuombera, vakarira, nokuparadza nyika yake; maguta ake akapiswa, hakuna unogaramo.
\v 16 Vana veNofi naveTapanesi vakapedza vhudzi romusoro wako.
\v 17 Ko hauna kuzvitsvaira izvozvo, zvawakasiya Jehovha Mwari wako panguva yaakakufambisa panzira yake here?
\v 18 Zvino unondotsvakei panzira inoenda Egipita, kundonwa mvura yeSihori here? Unondotsvakei panzira inoenda Asiriya, kundonwa mvura yoRwizi here?
\v 19 Zvakaipa zvako zvinokurova, kudzokera kwako shure kunokutuka; naizvozvo zvanzi nalshe Jehovha wehondo, Ziva, uone kuti chinhu chakaipa chinovava kuti wakasiya Jehovha Mwari wako, uye kuti haundityi.
\p
\v 20 Nokuti yatova nguva huru yawakavhuna joko nokudambura zvisungo zvako ukati,handidi kubatira;nokuti wakafugama pachikomo chipi nechipi chakakwirira pasi pomuti upi noupi mutema uchifeva.
\v 21 kunyange zvakadaro ndakange ndakusima uri muzambiringa wakaisvonaka, mbeu kwayo yazvokwadi; zvino wandishandukira sei ukava matavi akaipa omuzambiringa worumwe rudzi?
\p
\v 22 Nokuti kunyange ukashamba nesoda, ukatora sipo zhinji, kunyange zvakadaro zvakaipa zvako zvakaita segwapa pamberi pangu; ndizvo zvinotaura Ishe Jehovha.
\p
\v 23 Ungareva seiko, uchiti, Handina kusvibiswa, handina kutevera vaBhaari? Cherekedza nzira yako pamupata, uzive chawakaita; uri hadzi yekamera inomhanya, inofamba nenzira dzayo;
\v 24 uri hadzi yembizi yakarovera renje, inofembedza mhepo nokushuva kwayo; ndiani ungaidzora pakuviga kwayo? Dzose, dzinoitsvaka, hadzinganeti; pamwedzi wayo dzinoiwana.
\v 25 Usatendera rutsoka rwako kufamba usina shangu, nehuro dzako kuva nenyota. Asi iwe wakati, Hazvina maturo; kwete, nokuti ndakada vatorwa, ndivo vandichatevera.
\p
\v 26 Mbavha sezvainonyadziswa kana yaonekwa, saizvozvo imba yaIsraeri yanyadziswa, ivo, namadzimambo avo, namachinda avo, navapristi vavo, navaporofita vavo;
\v 27 ivo, vanoti kudanda, Uri baba vangu; nokubwe, Ndiwe wakandibereka; nokuti vakandifuratira, havana kunditarira nezviso zvavo; asi panguva yokutambudzika kwavo vachati, Simukai, mutiponese.
\p
\v 28 Zvino varipiko vamwari venyu vamakazviitira? Ngavasimuke kana vachigona kukuponesai panguva yokutambudzika; nokuti kuwanda kwavamwari vako, iwe Jakove, kwakaenzana namaguta ako.
\p
\v 29 Munokakavara neni neiko? imwi mose makandidarikira ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\v 30 Ndakarova vana venyu pasina, havana kuteerera kurangwa; munondo wenyu ndiwo wakauraya vaporofita venyu, seshumba inoparadza.
\v 31 Haiwa, imwi rudzi rwakadai! Wonai shoko raJehovha. Ko ini ndakange ndiri renje kuna Israeri here? Kana nyika yerima guru here? Vanhu vangu vanorevereiko vachiti, Tinongomberereka hedu, hatichazouyizve kwamuri?
\v 32 mhandara ingakanganwa zvishongo zvayo, kana mwenga mukonde wake here? Asi vanhu vangu vakandikanganwa mazuva asingaverengwi.
\v 33 Haiwa, unoziva zvakanaka sei kunatsa nzira yako, kuti utsvake kudikanwa ! Saka wakadzidzisa navakadzi vakaipawo nzira dzako.
\v 34 Pamipendero yenguvo dzako pakawanikwawo ropa ravarombo vasina mhaka; handina kuvawana vachipaza, asi pane zvizvi zvese.
\v 35 Kunyange zvakadaro iwe wakati, Handina mhaka; zvirokwazvo kutsamwa kwake kwakadzorwa kwandiri. Tarira, ndichakutonga, zvaunoti, Handina kutadza.
\v 36 Unofambireiko pose-pose, uchishandura nzira yako? Uchanyadziswa neEgipita, sezvawakanyadziswa neAsiriya.
\v 37 Naipapowo uchabva wakaisa maoko ako pamusoro wako; nokuti Jehovha wakaramba vaunovimba navo, newe haungabatsirwi navo.
